h2. 6-Layer Architecture

{panel:title=Layer 1: User Layer|borderColor=#3b82f6|bgColor=#eff6ff}
*Browser (QA Engineer)*
* React SPA hosted on Amplify + CloudFront CDN
* Cognito login -> JWT token -> Identity Pool -> scoped IAM role
* 4 screens: Agent, Inventory, Config, Admin
{panel}

{panel:title=Layer 2: Frontend & Delivery|borderColor=#8b5cf6|bgColor=#faf5ff}
|| CloudFront || Amplify || Cognito || IAM Roles || Secrets Manager || CloudWatch ||
| CDN / Distribution | Hosting + CI/CD | User Auth + Groups | Scoped permissions | Aurora credentials | Logs & monitoring |
{panel}

{panel:title=Layer 3: AI / Intelligence Layer|borderColor=#f97316|bgColor=#fff7ed}
|| Bedrock AgentCore || Claude Sonnet 4.5 || Strands SDK Tools ||
| Runtime Executor | LLM Inference | get_service_config, resolve_config |
| Runs agent container | Generates test plans | Connects to DynamoDB + MCP |
{panel}

{panel:title=Layer 4: Compute Layer|borderColor=#ef4444|bgColor=#fef2f2}
|| ECS Fargate || ECR (Agent) || ECR (Playwright) || Lambda (x3) ||
| On-demand tasks | prompt2test-agent | prompt2test-playwright-mcp | writer, reader, schema-init |
| ARM64 2vCPU/4GB | AI agent image | Chromium + noVNC image | Python 3.12 |
{panel}

{panel:title=Layer 5: Data & Storage|borderColor=#14b8a6|bgColor=#f0fdfa}
|| Aurora Serverless v2 || DynamoDB || RDS Data API || S3 ||
| PostgreSQL + pgvector | prompt2test-config | HTTP-based SQL access | Pipeline artifacts |
| test_cases, run_records | Services, accounts per team/env | No VPC needed for Lambda | CodeBuild output |
{panel}

{panel:title=Layer 6: CI/CD & DevOps|borderColor=#64748b|bgColor=#f8fafc}
|| GitHub (5 repos) || Amplify CI/CD || CodePipeline (x3) || CodeBuild || KMS ||
| Source code | UI auto-deploy | Lambda, Agent, Playwright | Docker + Python builds | Artifact encryption |
{panel}

----

h2. Data Flow

h3. Test Authoring Flow (Blue arrows)

|| Step || From || To || Protocol ||
| 1 | Browser | Amplify / CloudFront | HTTPS |
| 2 | Browser | Cognito | HTTPS (auth) |
| 3 | Browser | Bedrock AgentCore | AWS SDK (InvokeAgentRuntime) |
| 4 | AgentCore | Claude Sonnet | Bedrock InvokeModel |
| 5 | AgentCore | DynamoDB | AWS SDK (get_service_config) |
| 6 | AgentCore | Browser | Streaming JSON response |

h3. Test Execution Flow (Green arrows)

|| Step || From || To || Protocol ||
| 1 | AgentCore | ECS Fargate | RunTask API |
| 2 | ECS Task | ECR | Docker image pull |
| 3 | AgentCore | Playwright MCP | SSE (MCP protocol) |
| 4 | Playwright | Chromium | Browser automation |
| 5 | noVNC | Browser | WebSocket (port 6080) |
| 6 | AgentCore | ECS | StopTask API |

h3. Data Persistence Flow (Orange arrows)

|| Step || From || To || Protocol ||
| 1 | Browser | Lambda (writer) | AWS SDK (Invoke) |
| 2 | Lambda | Aurora | RDS Data API (SQL) |
| 3 | Lambda | Bedrock | InvokeModel (embeddings) |
| 4 | Browser | Lambda (reader) | AWS SDK (Invoke) |
| 5 | Lambda | Aurora | RDS Data API (query) |

h3. CI/CD Flow (Gray arrows)

|| Step || From || To || Trigger ||
| 1 | Developer | GitHub | git push |
| 2 | GitHub | CodePipeline | Webhook |
| 3 | CodePipeline | CodeBuild | Automatic |
| 4 | CodeBuild | ECR / Lambda | Docker push / Lambda update |
| 5 | GitHub | Amplify | Auto-deploy on push |

